{"body": "This is a REALLY bad idea - raising in index_name means the migration will fail, and that the DB will be left in a state requiring manual recovery on DBs that don't have transactional DDL (MySQL and Oracle, at least).\r\n\r\nSee the original ticket for the index length limit stuff for more details:\r\nhttps://rails.lighthouseapp.com/projects/8994/tickets/3452\r\n\r\nCode-wise, it's very difficult to follow exactly what's going on in there with all of the 'if options[:name]' etc. Perhaps it would be cleaner to split the logic for \"check the given name\" apart from \"compute and then check the name\"?", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/2750553", "created_at": "2011-11-15T20:15:28Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/1993#issuecomment-2750553", "updated_at": "2011-11-15T20:15:28Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 1993, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/al2o3cr", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/6883e5ef03484d4fcef507d7b4f1d243?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fb20bb95ab626d93fd976af958fbc61ba.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr/received_events", "gravatar_id": "6883e5ef03484d4fcef507d7b4f1d243", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "al2o3cr", "type": "User", "id": 1191, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/al2o3cr/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523fe6c0bd354364b901c1c2"}, "id": 2750553, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/rep